# Copy to .env.local and fill in your token (never commit .env.local).
#
# Required for Samantha chat (LLM) and useKV persistence in local dev.
# The @github/spark Vite plugin proxies /_spark/* using this token.
#
# Create a GitHub personal access token (classic or fine-grained) with access to:
#   - GitHub Spark runtime for app 18143a3391751b107150
#   - GitHub Models (models.github.ai)
#
# Cursor Cloud agents: add the same value as a secret named GITHUB_TOKEN
# (not "Samantha" or other names — the Spark plugin only reads GITHUB_TOKEN).
GITHUB_TOKEN=
